OL,3,C'We worry we'll be forgotten' - Rugby
OL,4,Cstar with motor neurone disease on
OL,5,Cillness
OL,7,FFormer Gloucester Rugby star Ed Slater
OL,8,Fhas said that people suffering with
OL,9,Fmotor neurone disease are worried
OL,10,Fabout being "forgotten".
OL,12,FThe 36-year-old was diagnosed with the
OL,13,Flife-limiting condition in 2022.
OL,15,FIt marked the end of his career as a
OL,16,Frugby player with the Cherry and
OL,17,FWhites but the start of his life as a
OL,18,Fcampaigner against the condition.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
