OL,3,C'We worry we'll be forgotten' - Rugby
OL,4,Cstar with motor neurone disease on
OL,5,Cillness
OL,7,FHe'll set off from the club's
OL,8,FKingsholm Stadium on Monday morning,
OL,9,Fvisiting Mattioli Woods Welford Road,
OL,10,Fthen continuing to Twickenham via
OL,11,FMilton Keynes RFC, before returning to
OL,12,FKingsholm on Tuesday.
OL,14,FHe'll be flanked by a support group
OL,15,Finvolving current club captain Lewis
OL,16,FLudlow and Fraser Balmain.
OL,18,FSpeaking at the start line, Ed said
OL,19,Fthat he hoped the event would keep the
OL,20,Fcondition in the public eye.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
