OL,3,C'We worry we'll be forgotten' - Rugby
OL,4,Cstar with motor neurone disease on
OL,5,Cillness
OL,7,FHe said: "This event is about friends
OL,8,Fcoming together, it is about keeping
OL,9,Fin the spotlight. There is a worry
OL,10,Fthat we will all get forgotten.
OL,12,F"There is no treatment, there is no
OL,13,Fcure and all you get is a thank you
OL,14,Fvery much before getting sent on your
OL,15,Fway. That is just not good enough."
OL,17,FBilly said of Ed: "He is one of the
OL,18,Fbest guys on the planet.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
