OL,3,C'We worry we'll be forgotten' - Rugby
OL,4,Cstar with motor neurone disease on
OL,5,Cillness
OL,7,F"He has been a teammate, he has been
OL,8,Fmy captain and he has been a true
OL,9,Fleader of men and he still is.
OL,11,F"We are going to go as hard as we can
OL,12,Ffor him and raise as much awareness
OL,13,Fand money for him as we can.
OL,15,F"He is going through a massive battle
OL,16,Fat the moment so we can keep going and
OL,17,Fcompete this ride in 24 hours so we
OL,18,Fcan all beat this horrible disease."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
