OL,4,Cstar with motor neurone disease on
OL,5,Cillness
OL,7,FLewis Ludlow, who also took part in
OL,8,Fthe 3-day charity bike ride event two
OL,9,Fyears ago, said: "Kingsholm does what
OL,10,FKingsholm does, fans packed in here to
OL,11,Fsee us off.
OL,13,F"We just hope we can get back here in
OL,14,Fthe time frame. Ed is a massive
OL,15,Finspiration, I look up to him in every
OL,16,Fway and how he deals with this.
OL,18,F"He is such a truly inspirational man.
OL,19,FThe great work of people in the MND
OL,20,Fcommunity so far is amazing.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
