OL,3,C'We worry we'll be forgotten' - Rugby
OL,4,Cstar with motor neurone disease on
OL,5,Cillness
OL,7,F"MND is not funded enough, we need to
OL,8,Fget it out there more and try and
OL,9,Fsupport this community."
OL,11,FJo Slater, Ed's wife, has been a key
OL,12,Fpart of the 4ED campaign group.
OL,14,FSpeaking at the event alongside Ed's
OL,15,Fmum, also called Jo, she said that she
OL,16,Fremains hopeful of a cure a they
OL,17,Fcontinue to come to terms with the
OL,18,Fcondition.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
