OL,3,C'We worry we'll be forgotten' - Rugby
OL,4,Cstar with motor neurone disease on
OL,5,Cillness
OL,7,FShe said: "In 24 hours I honestly
OL,8,Fdon't know how they are going to do it
OL,9,Fbut I just know that they will because
OL,10,Fthey are all amazing.
OL,12,F"I just think one day we can find a
OL,13,Fcure for the condition which would be
OL,14,Fthe best thing.
OL,16,F"In the meantime though we just need
OL,17,Fto keep banging the drum and raising
OL,18,Fas much awareness as we can.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
