OL,7,F"We need to make sure we are all heard
OL,8,Fbecause we are all together on this
OL,9,Fjourney."
OL,11,FThe money raised from the cycling
OL,12,Fchallenge will be split between
OL,13,Fvarious MND foundations and charities.
